lead_paragraph: Keyona Hayes scored 23 points, Jessica Thomas added 16 and No. 18 Miami outlasted No. 9 Ohio State 94-89 in overtime Thursday night in the ACC/Big Ten Challenge.

headline.print_headline: No. 18 Miami Upsets No. 10 Ohio State in Overtime 94-89
